full_summary:
### Government Tender Announcement: Power Generators

#### Tender Details

*   **Tender Reference:** [WS3561040885](#ws3561040885)
*   **Tender Title:**
    *   English: 60kW Propane Powered Standby Generator
    *   French: Génératrice de secours au propane de 60 kW
*   **Publication Date:** 2022-08-24
*   **Tender Closing Date:** 
    *   Note: The original Ariba Discovery posting response deadline closing time was disregarded. New closing time is October 3, 2022 at 16:00 EDT. 

#### Tender Overview

The Parks Canada Agency is seeking the supply and delivery of one (1), minimum 60 kilowatt skid mount standby generator powered by propane (LP) gas. This generator is required to support town operations in supplying potable drinking water for Park’s Canada Staff, the public, and for fire protection. The supplier will be responsible for delivering the generator to the water pumphouse facility located in the townsite of Waskesiu Lake, Saskatchewan, and then removing the old generator and installing the new generator in the existing building.

#### Contract Details

*   **Contracting Entity:** Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC/SPAC)
*   **End User Entity:** Parks Canada Agency (PC)
*   **Location:** Prince Albert, Saskatchewan
*   **Notice URL:**
    *   English: http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/13921190?extsite=MTM5MjExOTBfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==
    *   French: http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/13921190?extsite=MTM5MjExOTBfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==

#### Contact Information

*   **Contact Person:** 
    *   Dino Cavalic
    *   dino.cavalic@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
*   **Available Trade Agreements:**
    *   Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

#### Required Documents

Please submit all required supporting documentation and bids by the new deadline of October 3, 2022 at 16:00 EDT. Late bids will be declared non-responsive.  The successful bidder will be required to supply a minimum 60 kW propane generator,
